-- Danish Aug retail sales index up 1.1 pct
-- 
-- Mon Sep 22, 2014 03:09AM EDT
-- None



COPENHAGEN, Sept 22 (Reuters) - The Danish retail sales index rose 1.1 percent in August from a year earlier, the statistics office said on Monday.

Retail sales rose 0.6 percent in August from the previous month, Statistics Denmark said.Aug 2014 July 2014 Pct. change yr/yr +1.1 +0.7** Pct. change mth/mth   +0.6  0.0***  ** Revised from an initial figure of +0.4 percent. *** Revised from an initial figure of -0.1 percent.